quiz.name: Week 1 Quiz
quiz.intro:
Overview

The purpose of this quiz is for you to apply what you have learned this week to relevant questions on those topics.

Submission Directions

  • To begin, click the Attempt now button below.
  • During the quiz, be sure to [[[[[ANY SPECIAL INSTRUCTIONS]]]]].
  • When you are finished answering the questions, click the Submit all and finish button.
  • Each individual is responsible for submitting the quiz. You will know that you have successfully submitted when you see a screen that reads [[[[[[[[TBD-CONFIRMATION MESSAGE]]]]]]]].

Important Details

  • Attempts: You are allowed [[[[[[[[[[#]]]]]]]]]] attempts at this quiz, with your [[[[[[[[[[highest/average/last]]]]]]]]]] score used to calculate your final grade for this quiz.
  • Time limit: There is a [[[[[[[[[[# minutes/hours]]]]]]]]]] time limit to complete each attempt at the quiz. 
  • Quiz Navigation: This quiz displays a question navigation legend with answered/unanswered . [[[[[[[[You [[[[[[[[will/will not]]]]]]]] be able to go back to previous pages as you work through the quiz.]]]]]]] Do not use the back button on your browser to navigate through the quiz.

Evaluation and Deadlines

For information on evaluation and deadlines, see the Week [[[[X]]]] tab, [[[[[[the [[[[Rubric Name]]]] Rubric]]]]]]], and the Course Policies page.
